--------
 README
--------
Description of the content of the package of the Golden Collection of 
aligned bi-texts between all combinations of Portuguese (PT), Spanish (ES),
French (FR) and English (EN): PT-EN, PT-ES, PT-FR, ES-FR, 
taken from the first 100 sentences of the common test set of the EuroParl
corpus (http://www.statmt.org/europarl/archives.html).

