-----------
 CONTENTS:
-----------

*.wa: 
	en-es_1-100.wa
	en-fr_1-100.wa
	en-pt_1-100.wa
	es-fr_1-100.wa
	pt-es_1-100.wa
	pt-fr_1-100.wa

Language-pairs annotations created with the annotation and visualization tool 
implemented by Chris Callison-Burch (University of Edinburgh) 

@InProceedings{Callison-Burch2004,
	Author = {Chris Callison-Burch and David Talbot and Miles Osborne},
	Title = {Statistical Machine Translation with 
	         Word- and Sentence-Aligned Parallel Corpora},
	Booktitle = {Proceedings of the 42nd Annual Meeting of the 
	             Association for Computational Linguistics (ACL-2004)},
	Address = {Barcelona},
	Year = {2004}
}

sentences/1-100-final.*
	1-100-final.en
	1-100-final.es
	1-100-final.fr
	1-100-final.pt

Sentences used for each of the languages.

